<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-C%C3%A1t/Nh%C3%A3n-nhi-m%E1%BB%8B-Vong-qu%E1%BB%91c-m%C3%B4ng-tr%E1%BA%A7n-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-Jbh7-oMIbpSjuXCoya1rWA">Nhãn nhi mị - Vong quốc mông trần từ - 眼兒媚－亡國蒙塵詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-C%C3%A1t/author-CMJZvOtcIdi2704zHERNgA">Triệu Cát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-v%C5%A9-th%C3%A1n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-FcWzM9R187Ql7EMOYNDoaA">Thu vũ thán kỳ 1 - 秋雨歎其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-d%C3%A3-%C4%91a-c%C3%A2u-c%E1%BB%A9c/poem-2n625Xo2FAIFbfXCnKJ6FA">Vô đề (Đại dã đa câu cức) - 無題（大野多鉤棘）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
